      static <V> Map<Sense<V>,​Number> disambiguate​(Map<V,​Map<Sense<V>,​Map<V,​Number>>> inventory, ContextSimilarity<V> similarity, Map<V,​Number> context, Collection<V> ignored)
      Disambiguate each element of the context by maximizing its similarity to the senses in the inventory.

      The method skips context keys marked as ignored.

      Type Parameters:
      V - the context element class
      Parameters:
      inventory - the sense inventory
      similarity - the similarity measure
      context - the context to disambiguate
      ignored - the ignored elements of context
      Returns:
      the disambiguated context
